以下有期徒刑，得併科 9 萬元以下罰金。\r\n前二項之未遂犯罰之。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/PCDM/110%2c%e5%af%a9%e6%98%93%2c1844%2c20220310%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"PCDM,110,審易,1844,20220310,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"審易","JNO":"1844","JDATE":"20220310","JTITLE":"侵占"}